Name: DoTeam
About the game: DoTeam is a survival game. You will play an expelled rabbit in the game and live alone in the game world. In this fantasy game world, you can defeat different monsters, collect items and obtain various resources needed for survival. You can unlock different weapons and props, build different buildings freely, and build your own base.
